Summary: driving home and witnessed 8 or more orange lights. i am use to helicopters and aircraft at rhe local base. this was neither.
trends: There has been one other sighting in Steilacoom

divs: Sighting DetailsI was driving when I first saw the orange balls of light. They were moving like no aircraft I have ever seen coming to and from the local air base. What really caught my attention was the number of objects, 8 maybe more. I can always hear the helicopters and planes, for the number of objects, no sound. My question, was this the military? They were not fly towards the bases normal flight pattern. did they show up on radar? Did the FAA receive any notification?
